Name:           Triton
Short Name:     triton
Level Required: 7

Description:
  The Triton is a humanoid creature from the Elemental Plane of Water,
  attacking with webbed claws, tail thrashes, and its trident.

Commands:
  - summon triton:  Summons it to you         (costs 20 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban triton:     Banishes it               (costs 20 sp)
